Step 1. Start
Step 2. Input User's Name, Hourly rate salary, Hourly rate deduction
Step 3. Display Name, Hourly rate salary, Hourly rate deduction
Step 4. Compute Gross Rate = Hourly Rate Salary * Hours Worked
Step 5. Compute Deduction = Gross Pay * Deduction Rate
Step 6. Compute Net Pay = Gross Pay - Deduction
Step 7. Display User's Name, Gross Rate, Deduction, and Net Pay
Step 8. Done
